Product Description

Perfect Time-saving Choice for Data Transmission

The sd card reader supports up to 5Gbps- 10X faster than USB 2.0 data transfer rate. UGREEN 2 Slots Card Reader USB 3.0 allows you to transfer 1GB files in seconds. Less time waiting, more time enjoying. In addition, the USB 3.0 connector is backward compatible with USB 2.0 port.

Simultaneously Read & Write 2 Card

It allows you to read and write 2 cards at the same time, great choice to save a lot of time.

Simplify Your Life

You'll be able to transfer data from your laptop, update your car sat-nav map, watch movies and pictures on the smart TV and enjoy music on home audio easily.

High-Capacity SD card reader

Build-in Hi-Q GL3224 chip, support up to 512G card capacity, 2X than others!

Safe and Reliable

Build-in fuse to provide the over-current and short-circuit protection, ensure a stable and secure data transmission.

Universal Compatibility

UGREEN SD card reader is widely compatible operating systems like Mac OS, Chrome OS, Windows 10 / 8.1 / 8 / 7 / XP / Vista, Linux,

allowing you to read flash cards on Macbook, PC, Smart TV, PS4 Pro, PS4, PS3, Xbox One, portable DVD player and other USB A Devices.

  • SD Slot: UHS-I SDXC / SDHC / SD / Extreme I III SD / Ultra II SD / MMC / RS-MMC / MMC Micro
  • Micro SD (TF) Slot: UHS-I Micro SD / TF / Micro SDXC / Micro SDHC

Kindly Reminder

This USB sd card adapter will read UHS-II memory cards at UHS-I speed.

The data transfer speed could be affected by multi-cards simultaneous reading.

Insert the Micro SD card upside down. For Micro SD card slot, just insert/extract card with one slight push.

Aluminum Finish with Protective Cap

  • The sd card reader is made of high quality aluminum alloy that is good for heat dissipation.
  • The cap protects the USB connection against dust, knock or bump.

Plug and Play

  • The card reader adapter is driver-free, just plug and play, convenient to use.

Mini and Slim for Travel On-The-Go

  • Compact and lightweight design makes this sdxc card reader easy to store even in your pocket.
  • The keychain design makes this USB SD Card Reader easy to take and never need to worry about loss.

      Warren T.D.
      4.0 out of 5 stars Solves a headache caused by poor Windows OS design
      Reviewed in the United States on June 14, 2020
      Verified Purchase
      This product allowed me to read the SD cards of my cameras after the internal card reader on my HP desktop glitched. When the card is inserted into the internal reader, Windows 10 signals an error, and insists that the card needs to be formatted. How many poor souls actually did that without realizing that they've then lost all their files, I don't know. In fact, the card is perfectly fine, as you can determine by using another PC or the cameras themselves.

      This is a known problem that finds its way on to Microsoft support pages, and independent tech pages. Yet none of the proposed solutions at those sites ever work, and they don't seem to work for anyone. I don't believe there to be anything wrong with the reader, just something messed up with the drivers and/or one of the various messed-up Windows updates. And as we all know, manufacturers including Microsoft make it very difficult to solve driver issues. Presumably doing so helps sell more new product.

      Rather than buying another internal card reader, I bought this plug-in USB-based reader. It worked perfectly first time and thus far every time. It's money I would rather not spend, but at least the headache has gone away. And of course this can be used on devices such as a Surface Pro that don't have an internal reader.
